-levine\/\">Sam Noble Museum, University of Oklahoma<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.ou.edu\/cas\/anthropology\/faculty-staff\/marc-levine\">Anthropology Department, University of Oklahoma<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Badillo.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-2547 alignright\" src=\"https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Badillo-273x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"149\" height=\"164\" srcset=\"https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Badillo-273x300.jpg 273w, https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Badillo-768x843.jpg 768w, https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Badillo-933x1024.jpg 933w, https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Badillo.jpg 1796w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 149px) 100vw, 149px\" \/>D<\/a>r. Alex Badillo, Co-Director (MADAP) and Project Researcher (MAGAP)<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.indstate.edu\/faculty-staff\/alex-badillo\">Department of Earth and Environmental Systems\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Indiana State University<\/a><\/p>\n<p><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Hammerstedt.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-2548 alignright\" src=\"https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Hammerstedt-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"152\" height=\"152\" srcset=\"https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Hammerstedt-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Hammerstedt-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/Hammerstedt-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/montealban.oucreate.com\/wp-content\/uploads\